editorialNotes.standard: When a much-loved Canadian icon launches an innovative way for us Canucks to get our Timmy’s faster and easier, well, it’s a natural Editors’ Choice. We love that the app’s simple, scrollable menu makes it easy to preorder exactly what we want. The app offers up the closest participating pick-up locations, complete with map and directions.
